title: Changeset 14739 (and later) are impossible to compile on native Plan 9
body:
by **pavel.klinkovsky**: 
> What steps will reproduce the problem?
It is enough to rebuild Go project (rev:14739 and later) in native Plan 9.

When compiling exp/locale/collate, the system fails.
The picture of the display attached.

Pavel
